Serena Williams Beats Ivanovic 6-3, 6-4, Reaches U.S. Open Quarterfinals

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-09-05T19:38:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-05/serena-williams-beats-ivanovic-6-3-6-4-reaches-u-s-open-quarterfinals.html
Serena Williams  tamed the wind and
16th-seeded Ana Ivanovic of  Serbia  to reach the quarterfinals of
the U.S. Open.  Williams, a 28th-seeded American, won 6-3, 6-4 to move on
to a match against Anastasia Pavlyuchenkova of  Russia , the 17th
seed.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  